{"type": "article", "id": 61500, "title": "90 年代风席卷米兰时装周，以及，百盛集团去年亏损 7930 万元 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2019-02-25T05:41:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 239, "name": "米兰时装周"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 574557, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190225133740cEkpNUPrsFH7zxCe.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻</h3><p><strong><a href=\"https://us.fashionnetwork.com/news/Ferragamo-chairman-says-luxury-shoemaker-not-up-for-sale,1071630.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Salvatore Ferragamo 否认出售</a></strong> | 该集团董事长 Ferruccio Ferragamo 于 2 月 24 日否认将出售品牌。新任 CEO&nbsp;Micaela Le Divelec 也表示对品牌重塑有信心。截至 12 月 31 日的 2018 财年内，该品牌销售额下滑 3.4% 至 13.4 亿欧元。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/business-news/retail/new-dior-u-s-site-heralds-major-e-commerce-rollout-1203046342/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dior 在美国官网推出全品类电商服务</a>&nbsp;</strong>| Dior 曾于去年 11 月 28 日在官网尝试销售男装创意总监 Kim Jones 与美国艺术家 Kaws 合作系列，并于 2 天内售空。2 月 21 日，该品牌将美国官网线上购物服务又扩展至成衣、手袋、鞋履、配饰、珠宝及钟表。去年，新 CEO Pietro Beccari 上任后，很快任命了首席数字官&nbsp;Jens Riewenherm，希望推动多渠道零售的发展。据 WWD 报道，全品类电商还将于今年内在中国及日本推出。</p><p><strong><a href=\"http://news.winshang.com/html/065/3702.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">百盛集团去年亏损 7930 万元</a>&nbsp;</strong>| 百盛集团 2018 年业绩公告显示，该集团 2018 年经营收入达 48.47 亿元，同比增长 3.6%；经营利润为 1.69 亿元，同比上涨 103.1%；归属母公司权益持有人净亏损为 7930 万元；同店销售下降 2.4%。合计销售所得款项总额下降 4.8% 至 151.95 亿元人民币，主要由于门店数的减少。</p><p>不过年报中也称，特许专柜销售继续成为销售<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://data.eastmoney.com/zlsj/\" rel=\"nofollow\">主力</a>，销售占商品销售总额约81.1%，余下 18.9% 则来自直销；化妆品与配饰类别销售强劲，带来的直接销售金额增加约 3.1 亿元；此外，集团转型为配套服务分配更多经营租赁面积，租金收入和其他经营收入增加了 1020 万元。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><strong><a href=\"https://in.fashionnetwork.com/news/Inditex-unveils-new-logo-for-Massimo-Dutti,1071359.html#.XHNx8pMzbUo\" rel=\"nofollow\">Inditex 集团旗下品牌 Massimo Dutti 也更换了 Logo。</a></strong></p><p>新 Logo 中字母“M”仍为无衬线字体，而字母“D”则保留了经典设计。该品牌还于本周推出了 2019 年“By Numbers”系列大片，由摄影师&nbsp;Lachlan Bailey 和曾与 Roberto Cavalli 以及 Isabel Marant 等品牌合作的&nbsp;Atelier Franck Durand 共同创作。</p><p>Logo 的变更被视为品牌数字化的重要一步。Inditex 集团曾表示将于 2020 年以前实现旗下品牌线上购物覆盖全球。去年上半年，Massimo Dutti 销售额为 8.11 亿欧元，高于上一年同期的 7.91 亿欧元，使得该品牌成为 Inditex 旗下仅次于 Zara、Bershka 和 Pull &amp; Bear 的第四大品牌。它将于 3 月发布 2018 财年年报。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225124244Dpt8wG3NuHvRmQSj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.475385\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>左侧为 App Logo，右侧为品牌新 Logo。</figcaption> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902251243513zhHpoMR8Zw9sQ4O.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666154\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Massimo Dutti 2019 campaign: By Numbers </figcaption> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://www.vansjapan.com/2019-feb-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vans 日本官网推出新鞋款 “TASSEL SLIP ON”。</a></strong><br></p><p>新鞋款将穗饰流苏设计与 slip-on 鞋型相结合，外底采用轻质科技材料，共有黑、白、米三色可选，售价为 8500 日元（不含税）。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225122544UAmyM0h846D5zPns.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.598667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225122541a2degynRGLCrXt80.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.598667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225122543CDGn1q4u86IThKJv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.598667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://nowre.com/fashion/398335/uniqlo-x-jw-anderson-19-chunxiaxiliezhengshidengchang/\" rel=\"nofollow\">UNIQLO x JW Anderson 19 春夏系列将于 3 月 7 日发售。</a></strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902251222362s3evcQ8yU1OBXqY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.501502\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225122235sbpTV9n3hH2RieWy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225122236msEZbBPz3efYdruG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.501502\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225122235l1wExg6OiJFH8G7T.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225122236dBk5xofGelAaX0M3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225122237GbancWKZxDqLvmAN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.501502\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902251222389kMbfQSUVejKXHcy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225122235PzpSC42iJUA8OK3s.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.501502\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>米兰时装周继续。</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/runway/fall-ready-to-wear-2019/milan/versace/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Versace 2019 秋冬：</a></strong></p><p>Versace 去年被 Michael Kors 母公司 Capri 控股以 22 亿美元收购。2019 秋冬是它被收购后发布的首个系列。以涅槃乐队的歌曲作为背景，90 年代盛行的 Grunge 风格贯穿全程：捆绑紧身胸衣、蕾丝吊带裙、过膝荧光色丝袜、衍缝棉衣等。新手袋系列“Virtus”也一同亮相。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225111717bSEDv1V3fQ6YtZ5T.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225111714GF94QJS8uNAvUEIH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225111713R1CPwar4IUFgWeZE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225111711kWtwM1aCx0EFIpfg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902251117111EMG4AsuaCHPjOiF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225111712zFgCkPL0Ybu2fRJT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225111712pZPLU2IkQaDibOwy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225111711rSy2zw7fU16oJMEk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225111712kq8MhEN92cerYaHC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225111712eSG71r3lvhamKOFQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225111713Z34FyrgzEcMWKuSH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902251117149amdlSsgL8YeOxWk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225111714RdEuUbVPTH6W421p.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225111714GREm3AP6gkqOaYZu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225111715VSryFcW2s9LZnutQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225111715SrtuyTfPVMZ60bqD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225111715ozFi2hbgAxaPvcBQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225111716ISot1l3TawOUjq5u.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225111716MBZTOtmhexHp1d8y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225111712cAy8pM2Px1FzKWS5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225111716wWfIRg8CK3ZolAUb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225111717A1NlwzdQ0Eevhprg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/fashion-news/shows-reviews/gallery/marni-rtw-fall-1203047042/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Marni 2019 秋冬：</a></strong></p><p>创意总监 Francesco Risso 为新系列提炼出两个关键词：neural（神经质）和 erotic（色情）。<br></p><p>流动感强的面料被解构成半裙，用金属环或带子连接起来。金属腰带和配饰环绕在腰侧或胸前，给整体造型增加了朋克感。大衣也被裁成不同部分，再重新拼接起来，搭配不对称半裙。印花及波尔卡点则仅用在剪裁更为简洁的长裙上。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902251128435jw7aqJb69RzNMH0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225112837il5849o0YHxUc7Iv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225112844EoIUatmrNklgDFOZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902251128416wCVrhpdM72v4Nqx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225113010MYdh5filBTNp89DJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225112842Lm3Z7dVYuTcXFxsA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225112837iw0RqQcS1lOv3Z57.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225112834MzKDgBXU7hqLcZOt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225112836zecSUvQ1tioCyEN5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225112843pPfWailBhGgw364T.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902251128376CR9VIpWgX1ncyNZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225112839g7SAmYD0elBCzUEO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225112843ZBCJs49Tjt78MNoc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225112840nLpHATWcDG7txMSv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/runway/fall-ready-to-wear-2019/milan/bottega-veneta/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bottega Veneta 2019 秋冬：</a></strong></p><p>这是 33 岁新任创意总监&nbsp;Daniel Lee 的首个系列。在 Shownote 中，设计师解释说他希望通过这个系列“赞美自由、自我表达和感性”。单品中既有闪亮的 H 型连衣裙、解构针织衫，也有将 Bottega Veneta 经典编织结合利落剪裁的大衣。</p><p>不过一切都令人联想起他的“导师”、前 CELINE 总监 Phoebe Philo。这让一些秀评人对他的“自我表达”持观望态度。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225112318w6ctDIogrCYTXmBS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225112253LS2sGPYu851Z0k9x.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225112211AVMX5F17dYUPiR9n.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225112212dGqMeh54pmifnPjl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225112224bAoWEjmJ5e9qihT4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225112224aRoS8XbLsejtg67i.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902251122156o5NjI2ipu1hUb0K.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225112221lwcQjvXAC0I7H94g.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902251122132ifBM0AtUvOn9Xkb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225112220xQ1VM0awmdRyctXs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190225112226A2irq9Pgxt6s0E3N.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201902251122271VznCJPat9yb4xDu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>题图为 <a href=\"https://mojeh.com/fashion/donatella-versace-fw19-collection/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Versace 2019 Fall</a></p>"}